{"tid":2270020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"玩真心話大冒險一親辣妹芳澤　男子忘情啪啪啪卻掉「套」慘挨告","createTime":"2020-11-03T23:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T04:03:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a77219fede6977340e8b82f08397f63be3036b13","tid":2270020,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T23:32:41.000Z","msg":"新北市1名詹姓男子去年花9000元找1名辣妹當鐘點情人，原本談天說地卻玩起「真心話、大冒險」，辣妹願賭服輸，幫詹男口交還進而「滾床單」，事後辣妹卻告詹男用毒品咖啡包迷姦她，涉犯加重強制性交罪嫌，士林地檢署偵辦發現詹男在2人愛愛時突然拔下保險套、卻不願多付錢，但無法證明2人嘿咻違反辣妹意願，將詹男不起訴，辣妹聲請再議，堅稱遭詹男性侵，高檢署認為全案已調查完備，駁回辣妹的再議確定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201104/4A6SLOHDMVFHJMQVPCDEHSR3OA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201104%2F4A6SLOHDMVFHJMQVPCDEHSR3OA%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=01c93988\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201104%2F4A6SLOHDMVFHJMQVPCDEHSR3OA%2F&h=6cd51b4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201104/4A6SLOHDMVFHJMQVPCDEHSR3OA/</a>"},{"pid":"89b82fd47c27a6ec2083b041a82850721cf1b202","tid":2270020,"uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T23:36:44.000Z","msg":"新北市+1"},{"pid":"ab9a8a75317fc6729659f763f65e4e09f0d98b63","tid":2270020,"uid":135496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T23:38:07.000Z","msg":"做女人真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877f8683cf4f836e259df9d249bff5d777329f9b","tid":2270020,"uid":228894,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T23:55:53.000Z","msg":"台妺真係咁易畀人屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244bc7886adc90cd7a960e7c3ca2a34a70686edf","tid":2270020,"uid":1654,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T00:02:39.000Z","msg":"士林地檢署偵辦發現詹男在2人愛愛時突然拔下保險套、卻不願多